Please stay inside Easter Sunday. You are legally allowed to go to church but please consider that it is normally a very busy time for churches. You'll be putting yourself and others at risk, while also helping us lose progress with slowing the spread of the virus.



There are plenty of church services online or being televised. Don't let someone convince you that your church has got some coronavirus killing technology that protects you when you enter.
